WEBVTT

00:00.033 --> 00:01.262
<i>Previously on "The Family"...</i>

00:01.287 --> 00:04.253
- Adam!
- Adam! Adam? Oh, God, Adam.

00:04.373 --> 00:05.431
What if it's not him?

00:05.466 --> 00:07.207
There's just been something
off about him.

00:07.275 --> 00:09.509
You're a drunk, and you are confused.

00:10.879 --> 00:12.607
Who's that?

00:14.249 --> 00:15.682
A friend.

00:15.717 --> 00:17.017
Reporter: Hank Asher,

00:17.052 --> 00:19.119
behind bars for more than 10 years,

00:19.154 --> 00:20.620
is back at home.

00:20.689 --> 00:23.608
I need to use Adam as bait.

00:24.326 --> 00:25.692
He's here. He sees him.

00:26.258 --> 00:28.294
He's not okay.
He's not okay. I know my son.

00:28.330 --> 00:29.696
I don't feel right. I...

00:29.731 --> 00:32.165
Doctor: The blockage was here,
right below his appendix.

00:32.200 --> 00:35.668
My son had his appendix out
when he was 5.

00:35.704 --> 00:36.703
Adam?

00:37.531 --> 00:38.638
Adam?

00:39.299 --> 00:40.274
Ben?

00:42.811 --> 00:44.001
Who is he?

00:44.746 --> 00:46.242
Is his name Ben?

00:46.937 --> 00:48.540
[Voice breaking] I'm so sorry, mom.

00:48.750 --> 00:50.683
What did you do?

00:54.877 --> 00:55.556
Oh, my God.

00:55.590 --> 00:57.657
Mom.

00:57.692 --> 00:59.292
Mom?

00:59.327 --> 01:02.562
Don't you have any idea
what you have done?

01:02.597 --> 01:04.307
Do you even understand...

01:04.343 --> 01:06.768
- We were falling apart, all of us!
- Do you understand?

01:06.842 --> 01:08.208
Do you understand what you've done?

01:08.243 --> 01:09.776
I don't know.
How could you possibly think...

01:09.811 --> 01:10.790
I thought I could make it better.

01:10.826 --> 01:13.880
- Oh, my God! Oh, my God! Oh, my God.
- I thought if I could just...

01:13.915 --> 01:15.715
if I could just bring him back...

01:15.751 --> 01:16.916
- God...
- And I did.

01:16.952 --> 01:18.331
And I did... I brought my brother back!

01:18.366 --> 01:20.391
No, it's not him!
It is not your brother!

01:20.426 --> 01:22.000
I thought I could fix it!

01:22.220 --> 01:25.521
Seeing you lose him was
the worst moment of my life.

01:25.557 --> 01:29.425
Oh, well, now you get
to see it all over again.

01:30.782 --> 01:32.929
Mom, wha... Mom...

01:32.964 --> 01:34.564
Mom, please.

01:34.599 --> 01:37.433
You shouldn't drive. You're too upset.

01:37.469 --> 01:40.670
What if someone sees you like this?!

01:40.705 --> 01:41.838
Oh, my God.

01:41.873 --> 01:43.306
That's why you did it.

01:43.341 --> 01:45.408
- What?
- To win the election.

01:45.443 --> 01:47.109
- That's not true.
- Oh, my God.

01:47.145 --> 01:48.077
- That's not true.
- What?

01:48.112 --> 01:49.679
That's not true.

01:49.714 --> 01:52.448
You were worried about name recognition.

01:52.484 --> 01:53.616
And now you're not!

01:53.651 --> 01:55.284
No, I just wanted... I wanted things

01:55.320 --> 01:57.620
- to go back to the way they were.
- Oh, my God.

01:57.655 --> 01:59.622
- I just...
- I never thought about the race.

01:59.657 --> 02:01.624
I don't believe that.
I don't believe it!

02:01.659 --> 02:04.293
I love you, mom.

02:04.329 --> 02:05.637
I don't believe that, either!

02:06.210 --> 02:07.964
Mom...

02:07.999 --> 02:09.763
He was with him!

02:09.949 --> 02:11.868
For 10 years, he was there!

02:11.903 --> 02:13.569
Do you think that matters?

02:13.605 --> 02:15.938
He helped him. He knew him!
He... he... he...

02:16.007 --> 02:18.150
Everything about him,
more than we ever did!

02:18.186 --> 02:19.509
But he's not my son!

02:19.544 --> 02:21.911
He made Adam's life bearable!

02:21.946 --> 02:23.913
Doesn't he deserve something for that?

02:23.948 --> 02:25.748
He is not my son!

02:25.783 --> 02:27.746
Your son is dead!

02:33.424 --> 02:34.775
And...

02:35.760 --> 02:37.549
And Ben is here.

02:39.171 --> 02:40.934
And he may not be Adam,

02:42.300 --> 02:45.197
but he's the closest thing we have.

